Minister Qi Cai visited to U.S. for seeking intelligent personnel, CUSCC actively promoted it\n\n

  	Qi Cai, the provincial Committee Standing Committee and the Minister of Organization Department visited to the U.S. and participate in the &ldquo;2011 Zhejiang Private Capital and Foreign Intelligence Personnel Docking Activities&rdquo;. President of China-U.S. Chamber of Commerce Wynn Wang attended the activity and had a cordial conversation with the views on Sino-U.S. talent exchange.
